* The [[Living Gate]], a ''[[portal]]'' to the [[Far Realm]] located in the Feydark below [[Cendriane]].{{Cite dragon/391/Watchers at the Living Gate|68}}
* [[Irith Tal]], the drow city of Matron Zarra, mother and enemy of Liria Valthorin, who still aspires to use her daughter's archfey blood as a weapon.<ref>{{Cite dragon/386/Channel Divinity: Corellon|64}}
